text:
Home » Photos » Faces at 2016 Vanguard Personality of the Year Awards Faces at 2016 Vanguard Personality of the Year Awards On 
Stunning faces of different personalities were witnessed at Vanguard personality of the year held on Saturday at Eko Hotel and suite in Lagos, Below are some photos of gorgeous personalities that graced the occasion. Erelu Abiola Dosumu and Captain Hosa Okunbo. From left, Prof. John Pepper Clark; former President, LCCI, Mr. Goodie Ibru and wife, Janet. From left: Alhaji Sani Zauro, Buhari Aliero and Dr. Haliru Bala. From left, Chief Patricia Arawore, Chief John Odeyemi, Mrs Kofo Odeyemi and Mr Ted Iwere. From left, Mr Andrew Rewane; Chief Andrew Oru; Mr Onajite Oru and Mr Emeka Ugwu-Oju. Business Development Manager, Abumet, Dr. Tony Moffoi and wife, Tina. From left, Mr. Emeka Omeru, Chief Joe Canyaeche, Eze Gabby Emeka Dimude, Eze Omeudo 1 and Chief Emma Onwuzulike. Dr Yemi Ogunbiyi (left) and Mrs Rita Amuka. From left, Mr Nnabuike Edechime, Chief Guy Ikokwu, Chief Sylvanus Olisanye Ebigwei,Vice-President General, Ohanaeze, Chief Fabian Onwughalu and Chief Nnamdi Nwigwe. From left: Tola Omole, Eunice Imadeobelo, Florence Egbeyemi and Bridget Jaja. From left, Mr Kola Abiola, Mr Kingsley Okunbor, and Mrs Bamidele Okunbor. From left: Olorogun Taleb Tebite, Martins Orim, Chief of Staff, Cross River State and Mr Alphonsus Ogar Eba, Director General, Due Process, Cross River State. From left, Mr Peter Arigbe, Mrs Rashidat Uvieghara and Mr Dotun Duro-Emmanuel. From left, Mr Peter Okundaye, and Chief Steve Oronsaye, former Head of Service of the Federation. From left, Dr Ugbodaga Yahaya; Mr Osoro Ojo, Director Osa’s Motors; Prince Iyobosa Aighobahi and Comrade Peter Anigbogu, National Chairman of Africans in Diaspora Assocation. From left: Pastor Osagie Ize-Iyamu and his wife Dr Idia. Nollywood actresses at the event Nwafor Polycarp
